"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-07-parisolympics-knight-wisdom-narrowly-misses-qualification-final\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Jamaica's Yona Knight-Wisdom just missed qualification Wednesday for what would have been his first-ever Olympic final in the 3m springboard event at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.57934526838175, \"rank\": 0.7245336348268979, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yona_Knight-Wisdom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yona Knight-Wisdom\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yona_Knight-Wisdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yona_Knight-Wisdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Knight-Wisdom finished 13th with 412.40 points in the semi-finals, just one place and a mere four points out of the top 12 who will advance to the medal round at the Games.\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the best place ever for the Jamaican in his three Olympic Games and he will be the first alternate in the final but it will leave a bitter taste in his mouth to have come so close.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 380, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8015009245891678, \"rank\": 0.23856815209716553, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had qualified for the semi-final with 382.90 points from Tuesday's first round and was scoring over 400m points in a major championships only for the third time in his career.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fifth round reverse 3 \\u00bd somersaults in the tuck position which carried a 3.5 degree of difficulty, his most difficult dive, where he only scored 52.5 points, knocked the 29-year-old UK born athlete out of contention after he was well set with some inspired diving in the early rounds.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999616341161562, \"rank\": 3.265687851073998e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He started well, scoring 74.40 in the first round on a forward 3 \\u00bd somersaults in the pike position and also had scores over 70.0 in the third and final rounds.-Paul A Reid  Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}]}"